&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Every sample, record, word, sentence, object, image etc in the Machine learning language is called vector. If we want to measure the similarity or dissimilarity between two data points then we need distance function.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Distance metrics play a crucial role in various machine learning algorithms, including clustering, classification, and anomaly detection. Different distance measures capture different types of relationships between data points.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>